# Environment Variables

## Required Variables

### Twilio (Optional - for real SMS)
TWILIO_ACCOUNT_SID=your_account_sid_here
TWILIO_AUTH_TOKEN=your_auth_token_here
TWILIO_PHONE_NUMBER=+1234567890

### Stripe (Optional - for real card transactions)
STRIPE_SECRET_KEY=sk_test_your_key_here

### Server Configuration
PORT=3000
NODE_ENV=development

### Frontend URL (for CORS in production)
FRONTEND_URL=https://your-app.vercel.app

## Notes
- Leave Twilio and Stripe variables empty to use simulation mode
- FRONTEND_URL should be set to your Vercel deployment URL in production
